  "about_item": [
    "【Dogs are naturally active】Designed for medium and large dogs, this heavy-duty crate is built with durable 0.8-inch thickened elliptical steel tubes and high-strength steel, offering a solid 72-lb structure for lasting security and comfort.",
    "【 Security & Quadruple-Lock Security】Backed by over 20 years of experience in heavy duty dog kennel manufacturing, served more than 200,000 pet households, we’ve engineered this dog cage with four vertical-locking latches—two on the top and two on the bottom of the front door. You may notice that most comparable products only come with one or two horizontal latches, which are far more likely to be accidentally knocked open by dogs. In contrast, our four vertical latches add four layers of robust protection, making escape nearly impossible—even for the smartest and strongest dogs.",
    "【Quality & Quadruple-Layer Pressed Wood】This xl dog crate is crafted from four-layer cross-laminated plywood. The exterior features a waterproof coating, allowing for easy cleaning with just a wipe of a cloth. Ensuring a safer long-term living environment for your dog. An inner load-bearing reinforcement layer, with a thickness of 0.6 inches, enables the top panel to support up to 300lbs,The base plate maximum load capacity 300 lb. Furthermore, the wooden floorboard is gentler on your dog's paws compared to metal plates, helping to reduce the risk of interdigital cysts. This design ensures your dog stays comfortable and content while resting.",
    "【Elegance & Fits Your Home, Holds Your Life】Choose white or black to match your home's style and show your good taste.It can be a coffee table for your drinks, a display for your favorite photos, a handy storage spot for dog food and toys, or a bedside table for your lamp and books. Equipped with 4 non-slip and noise-free, adjustable foot pads to protects floors (height adjustable within 1.2-1.8 inches) Letting your furry friend integrate perfectly into your family for constant companionship.",
    "【Usage Tips】Leaving the dog crate door open during the initial stages can help your dog acclimate to the new environment more quickly. Only need to install 4 panels and 2 wooden boards. We include clear photo instructions and offer 24/7 customer support ready to help in real time.If you have any questions, please feel free to contact us.Our goal is to provide lasting care for your furry companion, not just a one-time purchase."
  ],
